import React from 'react'; import * as Styled from './TextCarousel.style' function TextCarousel() { return (
  1. Go to last slide Go to next slide
  2. Go to previous slide Go to next slide
  3. Go to previous slide Go to next slide
  4. Go to previous slide Go to first slide
  1. Go to slide 1
  2. Go to slide 2
  3. Go to slide 3
  4. Go to slide 4
) } export default TextCarousel // $('#arrow-down-slider').on('click', function() { // $('html').animate({ // scrollTop: $('#wallpaper').offset().top // }, 1000); // });
